Description: Tools for checking, preparing and analysing RCG template data
    (landings CL and sampling CS) from Mediterranean and Black Sea fisheries,
    developed in the RDBFIS III project Activity 10 by the stat4RDBFIS Core
    Team. The package includes validation of landings and sampling templates,
    crosschecks between datasets, preparation and raising of landings and
    discard LFDs, country-specific raising methods, age-length key estimation,
    discard ratio estimation, and routines for maturity and sex-ratio outputs.
